# deserializeModuleEntity

Deserializes a hexadecimal string into a `ModuleEntity` object containing a module address and an entity ID.

## Import

```ts
import { deserializeModuleEntity } from "@account-kit/smart-contracts";
```

## Usage

```ts
const entity = deserializeModuleEntity(
  "0xAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA000004D2"
);
```

## Parameters

### hex

`Hex`
The 24-byte hexadecimal string, prefixed with `0x`, representing the module entity

## Returns

`ModuleEntity`
An object containing the module address and entity ID
